commitResults.messageTitle: Create foundational files for relate command

Add IDContainsDigitsPredicate and RelatedList data structure Update classes: - RelateCommand - RelateCommandParser - NetConnectParser - PersonTuple - RelateStorage Design decision made here to store related data structure outside of UniquePersonList/InternalList

## Changes made: - Update save and load method in RelateStorage - Update PersonTuple to IdTuple, and propagate changes: Reason for change: to avoid propagation complexities due to changes to fields within the Person class, where if not propagated, will lead to inconsistencies in the calling of Person1.equals(Person1) where a single field has been changed. This also avoids the need to recreate the Person object from storage, which is computationally expensive and verbose compared to just storing the ID.
Integrate save and load of RelateStorage upon init in MainApp and StorageManager Create methods to both parse and write stored RelatedList to/from .txt file
Update implementation of Relate: - To follow existing NetConnect architecture more closely
